data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. NEW PRICE in Whitlock Community!! Fantastic opportunity to become the proud owner of this well maintained residence nestled within the highly sought-after gated community of Meadow Pointe III. This outstanding home welcomes you with soaring ceilings and a warm, inviting hallway that gracefully ushers you into the expansive family room. The generously sized kitchen offers seamless access to the family room and showcases elegant granite countertops, a charming apron sink, and an expansive breakfast bar. The master suite is a true retreat, featuring an ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, an oversized shower, and convenient access to the spacious walk-in closet. The two additional spacious bedrooms share a well-appointed hall bathroom, conveniently situated between them. Step outside onto the delightful screened porch, which leads to your own private backyard, where you can immerse yourself in the beauty of nature. Meadow Pointe provides an array of outstanding amenities, including a clubhouse, an Olympic-sized pool, an exhilarating water slide, a fitness center, a playground, and a park. Conveniently located near I-75 and 275, this home is also within close proximity to shopping, restaurants, golf courses, and a medical center. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to live in a vibrant and well-connected community.
